g'_{\text{avg}}=\frac{1}{a-1}\int_{1}^{a}\frac{\mathrm{d}g(x)}{\mathrm{d}x}\:\mathrm{d}x=\frac{g(a)-g(1)}{a-1}=\frac{\frac{1}{a}-1}{a-1}=-\frac{1}{a}
