\frac{\frac{1}{a}-1}{a-1}=\frac{\frac{a}{a}-a}{a^{2}-a}=\frac{1-a}{a^{2}-a}=\frac{1-a}{a(a-1)}=-\frac{a-1}{a(a-1)}=-\frac{1}{a}
